  "1709880": {
    "name": "罗伊斯号快车谋杀案",
    "steam_appid": 1709880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/43e7d9cce7e4e4be9aeebfd34a2870af.webp?t=1770924597\" width=616 height=37 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/00a6bec0cd38be582aa60a29e4d39e56.avif?t=1770924597\" width=616 height=103 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/0c2848dd2c25a0ffaf1b226c290c3af3.poster.avif?t=1770924597\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/0c2848dd2c25a0ffaf1b226c290c3af3.webm?t=1770924597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/0c2848dd2c25a0ffaf1b226c290c3af3.mp4?t=1770924597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎乘坐罗伊斯号特快列车，原本只是稀松平常的出行，将会因突如其来的谋杀案变成毕生罕有的经历。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豪门千金翁特瓦尔德夫人即将发表重要讲话，一位律师、一名侦探与一名卧底间谍却在这个时候卷入了一场杀人疑案和一段冒险！律师古板保守，侦探入行不久，原为犯罪小说作家，两人将与间谍一同困在这列豪华的蒸汽火车。冷血杀手与他们仅有一臂之遥，看看谁能率先彻底证明自己的清白！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身戴安娜、亚瑟、赫尔曼，拨开谜云，搬出你指向点击的解谜本领……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/8d7e91ccdc23d580a95d0fb5d3cd9f13.avif?t=1770924597\" width=616 height=103 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/bcd812e122797f462e3920b877259b34.poster.avif?t=1770924597\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/bcd812e122797f462e3920b877259b34.webm?t=1770924597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/bcd812e122797f462e3920b877259b34.mp4?t=1770924597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜剧冒险，仿佛丝滑的爵士乐，在1930年代的特快列车上娓娓展开 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控三个角色，体验这段喜剧冒险错纵交织的剧情 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受故事的荒诞滑稽与跌宕起伏，拨开险象环生的谜雾 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邂逅满满一车稀奇古怪而又可疑的乘客 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >竭尽全力，利用各种物品破解谜题，绝对不会让你苦思冥想几个小时 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你来决定自己的游戏方式，可以直接控制可以互动的角色，也可以选择经典的指向点击模式 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像素美术细致入微，游戏动画精美别致 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >稍微需要一点点灵感吗？游戏内设一条热线，专门向您提供提示！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音效丝滑，节奏鲜明，出自《Wildfrost》与《雪居之地》作曲家Paul Zimmerman之手  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英文配音！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/7e923db44f1cc5485a9cb8411807ea13.poster.avif?t=1770924597\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/7e923db44f1cc5485a9cb8411807ea13.webm?t=1770924597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/7e923db44f1cc5485a9cb8411807ea13.mp4?t=1770924597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709880/extras/27341107ac7468021d3d5f39971c86b2.webp?t=1770924597\" width=616 height=37 /></span></p>",
